'''The Teeth of Tatooine''' was a rarely performed but much enjoyed type of execution for [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]].

A prisoner was tied up and left to face wind currents in [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine's]] [[Valley of the Winds]]. The area's sand tides would lift sand deposits and small stones, throwing them with such velocity that they would cut into the skin of a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]]. They were effectively slashed to death.

[[Dengar/Legends|Dengar]], the last man to ever be condemned in this fashion by Jabba, escaped, preventing what would have been a slow and painful demise.

